{"tid":1153820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夾公仔機陷阱","createTime":"2019-05-14T01:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T06:38:35.000Z","uid":49609,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7201ca88920eefa5b098e72a4d954ff20f67405a","tid":1153820,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:16:36.000Z","msg":"已有前科被指誤導投資者作大額投資的股評人兼網絡紅人火燎森，再次捲入同類事件。逾100名市民向政黨求助，指誤信火燎森推介，花8.5萬至超過160萬元不等投資夾公仔機，總額涉及超過3,000萬元，但回報卻與當初聲稱有很大出入，逾30名苦主已向警方報警求助。本報就事件向火燎森查詢，暫未獲回應。<br />\n今日11名苦主聯同民主黨召開記者會，民主黨財經政策副發言人袁海文表示，自去年11月至今共收到超過100名苦主求助，該批苦主全都是受到火燎森的誤導而對夾公仔機作出大額投資，每部夾公仔機約8.5萬至10萬元。<br />\n袁海文指，當初苦主們由於誤信火燎森的推介，故展開投資，「當時佢吹噓每個月嘅回報有1萬蚊，最後半年先得幾十蚊回報，有啲苦主曾經因爲聽取火燎森嘅投資建議而喺虛擬貨幣有短期獲利，同埋聽到如果投資夾公仔機，未來投資其他機種有優先嘅投資權」，令苦主認為機不可失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190513/59595230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F59595230&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=46f1ae70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190513%2F59595230&h=a588332d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190513/59595230</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af220ce4e01306c090bb27c297de49a2a6d90d53","tid":1153820,"uid":253005,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47d2ce4aff687359cc64337e88d55353fb6a60b0","tid":1153820,"uid":66811,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"條友咁出名都仲有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ca2b165e25f1baa9afa200b01a3